<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Agregar Producto</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Mejoras específicas para el formulario */
        .form-card {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .form-card .card-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .form-group label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        .form-group label .required {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .form-group .hint {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #888;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
        }
        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: #fafafa;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #1a2a6c;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(26, 42, 108, 0.1);
            background: white;
        }
        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 0;
            }
            .form-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e, #38ef7d);
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }
        .btn-success:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(17, 153, 142, 0.4);
        }
        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: #1a2a6c;
            border: 2px solid #1a2a6c;
        }
        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: #1a2a6c;
            color: white;
        }
        .icon-input {
            position: relative;
        }
        .icon-input .icon {
            position: absolute;
            left: 1rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .icon-input .form-control {
            padding-left: 2.8rem;
        }
        .badge-info {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e8f0fe;
            color: #1a2a6c;
            padding: 0.2rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">📊 <span>Contabilidad</span></a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/inventario" class="active">📦 Inventario</a>
                <a href="/ventas">💰 Ventas</a>
                <a href="/contabilidad">📊 Contabilidad</a>
                <a href="/facturas">🧾 Facturas</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="form-card">
            <div class="card-title">
                ✨ Agregar Producto
                <span style="display: block; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 400; color: #888; margin-top: 0.3rem;">
                    Completa los datos del nuevo producto
                </span>
            </div>

            <form method="post" action="/api/productos">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>
                        📝 Nombre <span class="required">*</span>
                        <span class="hint">Ej: Arroz, Leche, Harina</span>
                    </label>
                    <input type="text" name="nombre" class="form-control" required placeholder="Nombre del producto">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>
                        🔢 Código <span class="hint">(dejar vacío para auto-generar)</span>
                    </label>
                    <input type="text" name="codigo" class="form-control" placeholder="Ej: A001, B010, etc.">
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            📁 Categoría
                            <span class="hint">opcional</span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" name="categoria" class="form-control" value="General" placeholder="General">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            📏 Unidad
                            <span class="hint">opcional</span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="text" name="unidad" class="form-control" value="u" placeholder="u, kg, litro, etc.">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            💰 Precio USD <span class="required">*</span>
                            <span class="hint">en dólares</span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="icon-input">
                            <span class="icon">$</span>
                            <input type="number" step="0.01" name="precio_usd" class="form-control" required placeholder="0.00" min="0">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>
                            📦 Cantidad <span class="required">*</span>
                            <span class="hint">stock inicial</span>
                        </label>
                        <input type="number" name="cantidad" class="form-control" required placeholder="0" min="0">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 10px; margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555;">
                    💡 <strong>Tip:</strong> Si dejas el código vacío, se generará automáticamente (ej: A001, B010, etc.)
                </div>

                <div class="btn-group">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">💾 Guardar Producto</button>
                    <a href="/inventario" class="btn btn-outline">❌ Cancelar</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>Sistema de Contabilidad Dual v5.0 &bull; Node.js</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
